{"type": "article", "id": 2576, "title": "Moleskine LEGO 2014 联名笔记本", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-26T08:14:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232238fqZpgilTktQFCvy6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t继 2012 年推出 Moleskine LEGO系列限量版笔记本后，Moleskine 与乐高日前再度联手推出全新笔记本，将乐高的经典积木嵌入了 Moleskine 的本子封面上。内页部分也融入了乐高积木的元素，激发人们在写字绘画时的灵感与创造力。这款 Moleskine LEGO 2014 联名笔记本共有 4 种颜色可选，售价 18.95 美元，<a href=\"http://shop.moleskine.com/en-us/special-collections/limited-editions/lego/lego-ii-2-limited-edition-notebook-pocket-plain-black-hard-cover-8075\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232235OtBkqDF1CpiMZo5m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232236AZr5D8ViW0elhFgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232236ZbAkcCxnTBgvhKsW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232237hbYatc1KpNFlfwdD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}